public interface Tuple1<A> extends Tuple
A tuple that always contains one element. More formally: T1 = (t0) or |T1| = 1. The Tuple1 interface extends Tuple and provides all his behaviour. The Tuple1 interface additionally provides one method for the accessing a tuple element using a getT0 getter.
